snippet.title: No More Snow | Demo Playthrough | PC
snippet.description:
Wishlist here: Wishlist here: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2244970/No_More_Snow/?utm_source=youtube
Download demo: https://barzda.itch.io/no-more-snow

No More Snow is a short game I created as a Christmas project during the covid quarantine. 
Santa has to face off his eternal enemy - a dark Christmas spirit called Krampus and his minions.

Dark and spooky Christmas music by composer Myuu (https://www.youtube.com/c/myuuji)
